{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-20",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_20_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 20 - If They Hang You",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 5,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 983.28,
  "page_end_sec": 1223.34,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.648,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 983.28,
      "end": 984.24,
      "text": "I should trust you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 984.66,
      "end": 985.26,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 985.38,
      "end": 985.6,
      "text": "no,"
    },
    {
      "start": 985.62,
      "end": 985.92,
      "text": "darling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 986.1,
      "end": 987.94,
      "text": "I wouldn't do it even if I could."
    },
    {
      "start": 988.7,
      "end": 989.632,
      "text": "Why should I?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 990.94,
      "end": 992.36,
      "text": "Her eyes were steady under his,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 992.62,
      "end": 994.88,
      "text": "and her hushed voice was steady when she replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 996.54,
      "end": 997.12,
      "text": "\"'Why should you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 997.6,
      "end": 999.4,
      "text": "If you have been playing with me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 999.54,
      "end": 1001.02,
      "text": "if you do not love me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1001.42,
      "end": 1002.2,
      "text": "there is no answer to"
    },
    {
      "start": 1002.32,
      "end": 1002.36,
      "text": "that."
    },
    {
      "start": 1002.58,
      "end": 1003.66,
      "text": "If you did,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1003.86,
      "end": 1005.44,
      "text": "no answer would be needed.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1007.16,
      "end": 1008.9,
      "text": "Blood streaked Spade's eyeballs now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1009.08,
      "end": 1010.84,
      "text": "and his long-held smile had become"
    },
    {
      "start": 1010.84,
      "end": 1011.8,
      "text": "a frightful grimace."
    },
    {
      "start": 1012.26,
      "end": 1014.34,
      "text": "He cleared his throat huskily and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1015.456,
      "end": 1017.52,
      "text": "\"'Making speeches is no damn good now.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1018.34,
      "end": 1019.52,
      "text": "He put a hand on her shoulder.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1020.22,
      "end": 1021.16,
      "text": "The hand trembled.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1022.22,
      "end": 1023.62,
      "text": "\"'I don't care who loves who.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1024.02,
      "end": 1026.06,
      "text": "I'm not going to play the sap for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 1026.26,
      "end": 1026.36,
      "text": "I"
    },
    {
      "start": 1027.24,
      "end": 1030.48,
      "text": "won't walk in Thursby's and Jacobi's and God knows who else's",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1030.7,
      "end": 1030.8,
      "text": "footsteps."
    },
    {
      "start": 1031.16,
      "end": 1033.84,
      "text": "You killed Miles and you're going over for it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1034.78,
      "end": 1035.2,
      "text": "I could have",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1035.2,
      "end": 1036.6,
      "text": "helped you by letting the others go"
    },
    {
      "start": 1036.6,
      "end": 1038.16,
      "text": "and standing off the police the best"
    },
    {
      "start": 1038.16,
      "end": 1038.78,
      "text": "way I could."
    },
    {
      "start": 1039.06,
      "end": 1040.32,
      "text": "It's too late now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1041.26,
      "end": 1042.06,
      "text": "I can't help you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1042.2,
      "end": 1043.98,
      "text": "and I wouldn't if I"
    },
    {
      "start": 1044.08,
      "end": 1044.512,
      "text": "could.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1045.78,
      "end": 1047.8,
      "text": "She put a hand on his hand on her shoulder.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1049.088,
      "end": 1050.98,
      "text": "\"'Don't help me then,' she whispered.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1050.98,
      "end": 1052.14,
      "text": "\"'But don't hurt me."
    },
    {
      "start": 1052.72,
      "end": 1053.08,
      "text": "Let me go"
    },
    {
      "start": 1053.2,
      "end": 1053.94,
      "text": "away now.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1054.44,
      "end": 1055.98,
      "text": "\"'No,' he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1056.896,
      "end": 1059.68,
      "text": "\"'I'm sunk if I haven't got you to hand to the police when they come.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1060.24,
      "end": 1061.86,
      "text": "That's the only thing that can keep"
    },
    {
      "start": 1061.86,
      "end": 1063.48,
      "text": "me from being sunk with the others.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1064.78,
      "end": 1066.1,
      "text": "\"'You won't do that for me?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1066.82,
      "end": 1068.34,
      "text": "\"'I won't play the sap for you.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1069.248,
      "end": 1069.84,
      "text": "\"'Don't say that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1069.92,
      "end": 1070.52,
      "text": "please.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1071.66,
      "end": 1074.12,
      "text": "She took his hand from her shoulder and held it to her face.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1075.58,
      "end": 1076.54,
      "text": "\"'Why must you do this,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1076.64,
      "end": 1076.86,
      "text": "Sam?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1077.536,
      "end": 1078.08,
      "text": "Surely Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1078.22,
      "end": 1080.06,
      "text": "Archer wasn't as much to you as—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1080.5,
      "end": 1082.94,
      "text": "\"'Miles,' Spade said hoarsely,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1083.56,
      "end": 1083.96,
      "text": "\"'was a—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1084.82,
      "end": 1087.8,
      "text": "I found that out the first week we were in business together,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1088.1,
      "end": 1090.62,
      "text": "and I intended to kick him out as soon as the year was up."
    },
    {
      "start": 1091.38,
      "end": 1093.952,
      "text": "You didn't do me a damn bit of harm by murdering him.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1095.06,
      "end": 1095.7,
      "text": "\"'Then what?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1096.832,
      "end": 1098.3,
      "text": "Spade pulled his hand out of hers.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1098.72,
      "end": 1101.16,
      "text": "He no longer either smiled or grimaced."
    },
    {
      "start": 1101.86,
      "end": 1104.8,
      "text": "His wet yellow face was set hard and deeply lined.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1105.54,
      "end": 1106.96,
      "text": "His eyes burned madly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1107.46,
      "end": 1107.86,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1108.52,
      "end": 1109.12,
      "text": "\"'Listen,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1109.86,
      "end": 1111.32,
      "text": "this isn't a damned bit of good.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1111.98,
      "end": 1113.6,
      "text": "You'll never understand me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1113.74,
      "end": 1116.24,
      "text": "but I'll try once more and then we'll give it up."
    },
    {
      "start": 1116.86,
      "end": 1118.26,
      "text": "In my part of the world,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1118.34,
      "end": 1119.4,
      "text": "when your partner's killed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1119.58,
      "end": 1121.26,
      "text": "you're supposed to do something about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1121.94,
      "end": 1123.94,
      "text": "It doesn't make any difference what you thought of him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1124.64,
      "end": 1125.46,
      "text": "He was your partner,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1125.58,
      "end": 1127.54,
      "text": "and you're supposed to do something about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1128.288,
      "end": 1130.78,
      "text": "Then it happens that we are in the detective business.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1131.68,
      "end": 1131.96,
      "text": "Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1132.14,
      "end": 1133.14,
      "text": "when one of your employees,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1133.52,
      "end": 1134.22,
      "text": "or a partner,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1134.38,
      "end": 1136.94,
      "text": "or anybody connected with your detective business is killed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1137.3,
      "end": 1139.94,
      "text": "it's bad business to let the killer get away with it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1140.8,
      "end": 1141.72,
      "text": "It's bad all around.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1142.44,
      "end": 1143.56,
      "text": "Bad for that one agency,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1143.74,
      "end": 1144.98,
      "text": "and bad for every detective."
    },
    {
      "start": 1145.26,
      "end": 1145.32,
      "text": "detective."
    },
    {
      "start": 1145.86,
      "end": 1146.6,
      "text": "Bad all around."
    },
    {
      "start": 1147.2,
      "end": 1148.12,
      "text": "Third,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1148.4,
      "end": 1149.22,
      "text": "I'm a detective,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1149.5,
      "end": 1152.12,
      "text": "and expecting me to run any criminal down"
    },
    {
      "start": 1152.32,
      "end": 1154.58,
      "text": "and then let him go free is like asking a"
    },
    {
      "start": 1154.58,
      "end": 1156.56,
      "text": "dog to catch a rabbit and then let it go."
    },
    {
      "start": 1157.22,
      "end": 1158.62,
      "text": "It can be done all right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1158.72,
      "end": 1160.0,
      "text": "and sometimes it is done,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1160.2,
      "end": 1161.9,
      "text": "but it's not the natural thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1163.94,
      "end": 1166.06,
      "text": "But—wait till I'm through and then you can talk.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1166.7,
      "end": 1167.3,
      "text": "Fourth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1167.48,
      "end": 1169.08,
      "text": "no matter what I wanted to do"
    },
    {
      "start": 1169.08,
      "end": 1169.28,
      "text": "now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1169.5,
      "end": 1171.58,
      "text": "it would be absolutely impossible for me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1171.58,
      "end": 1173.38,
      "text": "to let you go now without having myself"
    },
    {
      "start": 1173.64,
      "end": 1175.62,
      "text": "dragged in with Gutman Cairo and the kid."
    },
    {
      "start": 1176.12,
      "end": 1176.94,
      "text": "Next,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1177.16,
      "end": 1179.7,
      "text": "I've got no reason in God's world to think I can"
    },
    {
      "start": 1179.82,
      "end": 1180.22,
      "text": "trust you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1180.38,
      "end": 1182.56,
      "text": "and if I did this and got away with it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1182.72,
      "end": 1185.22,
      "text": "you'd have something on me that you could use if"
    },
    {
      "start": 1185.22,
      "end": 1186.28,
      "text": "you ever happened to want to."
    },
    {
      "start": 1187.296,
      "end": 1188.14,
      "text": "That's five of them.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1188.98,
      "end": 1190.0,
      "text": "The sixth would be that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1190.06,
      "end": 1191.22,
      "text": "since I'd also have"
    },
    {
      "start": 1191.32,
      "end": 1191.92,
      "text": "something on you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1192.18,
      "end": 1195.58,
      "text": "I couldn't be sure you wouldn't decide to shoot holes in me some day."
    },
    {
      "start": 1196.2,
      "end": 1196.8,
      "text": "Seventh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1197.2,
      "end": 1199.4,
      "text": "I don't like the idea of even thinking that there"
    },
    {
      "start": 1199.4,
      "end": 1201.44,
      "text": "might be one chance in a hundred that you'd play"
    },
    {
      "start": 1201.6,
      "end": 1202.18,
      "text": "be for a sucker."
    },
    {
      "start": 1203.6,
      "end": 1204.08,
      "text": "And eighth,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1204.28,
      "end": 1205.3,
      "text": "but that's enough."
    },
    {
      "start": 1206.02,
      "end": 1207.12,
      "text": "All those on one side.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1208.192,
      "end": 1208.98,
      "text": "Maybe some of them",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1209.02,
      "end": 1209.7,
      "text": "seem unimportant,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1210.24,
      "end": 1211.28,
      "text": "but look at the number of them."
    },
    {
      "start": 1212.18,
      "end": 1214.02,
      "text": "Now on the other side we've got what?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1214.9,
      "end": 1217.12,
      "text": "All we've got is the fact that maybe you love me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1217.3,
      "end": 1218.752,
      "text": "and maybe I love you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.22,
      "end": 1221.82,
      "text": "\"'You know,' she whispered,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1221.88,
      "end": 1223.34,
      "text": "\"'whether you do or not.'"
    }
  ]
}